The operands of each instruction in each lane Operands&#91;op&#95;index&#93;&#91;lane&#93;.

Note: This helps avoid the replication of the code that performs the reordering of operands during buildTree&#95;rec() and <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/slpvectorizer/boupslp/#af30798297200e0134c0a54cfdfa6c6cd">vectorizeTree()</a>.
